                                     <strong>Treyding. Aңyzdar men Shyndyқ!</strong><p><span>  </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span></span></figcaption></figure><h2><span><b>Barlyқ қoldaymyz!</b></span></h2><p><span><b>Ghiі</b></span><span> kөruge bolady gharnamalyқ suretter, қay gherde, teңіz ghaғasynda, astynda palymoy, sidit adam kerek қazaқstan shezlonge ghәne importty қor birghasy. Shamasy, bұl ghasauғa tiіs әser gheңіldіgі ghәne қarapayymdylyғy treyding, қol ghetіmdіlіk </span><span><i>"әdemі өmіr"</i></span><span> astynda palymoy. Gharnamalyқ suretter қatty erekshelenedі naқty өmіr.</span></p><p><span><b>Adamdardyң kөpshіlіgі</b></span><span>, kіm aynalysady treydingom ghәne investiciyalarғa, bar ghұmysty nemese bar, ol үshіn olardyң negіzgі bolyp tabylady. Investiciyalar olar үshіn, bұl tezіrek ghanama tabys nemese әyteuіr bіr </span><span><i>"oyynshyқ"ghan</i></span><span>boluy mүmkіn, hobbi perspektivasymen boluғa nәrse kerek emes. Men ғana өte shaғyn bөlіgі investorlardy tabuғa, өzіne өmіrі tek treydingom nemese өzіnің biznespen investiciyalarmen baylanysty.</span></p><p><span><b>Sonymen kerneulі</b></span><span> қazіr, torguya shotynda, bіz ghұmys іstedі eshқashan. Ghұmys kүnі bastalyp, shamamen taңғy saғat 7-den bastap oқyғannan ghaңalyқtar, analitikalyқ maқalalar men ayaқtalady, keyde shamamen 24 saғat, eger naryғyndaғy ghaғday shielenіstі. Bүtіn kүn bіz aldynda monitorlarmen, taldaumen aynalysyp, tүrlі sauda құraldaryn, oқimyz ghaңalyқtar, ұyym ghasaytyn sauda operaciyalary, ghazamyz maқalalar ghәne beynerolikter pro sauda ghәne treyding ghүrgіzemіz, gheke oқytu. Basқasha aytқanda, uaқyt ghaғaghay ghәne palymu ғana қalady. Iә, әrine, bіz bere alasyz ustroity demalys, bіraқ tek uaқytsha prekrativ өzіnің belsendі қyzmetі. </span><span><b>Treyding talap etedі ghasalyndy. </b></span></p><p><span><b>Әrine</b></span><span>, өz artyқshylyғy bar ghұmysynda өzіne. Salyқtar nebәrі </span><span><b>13% tabys ghәne bұl barlyқ</b></span><span>. Kezde Sіz </span><span><i>"bіreuge",</i></span><span> yaғni tabys salyғynan basқa, Sіzdің ghұmys berushі tөleydі taғy </span><span><b>shamamen 45% salyқtardy, Sіzdің ghalaқy әr tүrlі қorlar</b></span><span>. Bұl ghay ғana tөleu ghasyryn kөptegen adamdar, ghәne, bіraқ, nezametny. Kөptegen elderde adamdar өzderі tөleydі өzіnің barlyқ salyқtar, ghәne anyқ kөrіp, olardyң өlshemі ghәne maқsaty. Emes өte tүsіnіktі, ne үshіn aқsha tөleuge, mіndettі zeynetaқy gharnalaryn, eger bұl zeynetaқyғa өmіr sүru mүmkіn emes. Nege memleket dep sanaydy, ol ghaқsy өkіm bіzdің aқshamen, eger bіz kүnde kөrіp mysaldar tiіmsіz shyғystar, ghemқorlyқ, ұrlyқ ghәne tұraқty өzgerіster zaңdar men ereghelerdі biznes ghүrgіzu. Bіz dayyn emes қarghylandyratyn mұnday tәsіl memleket өz aқshasyn, sondyқtan </span><span><b>13%) tabystar dep sanaymyz әdіl tөlem</b></span><span>үshіn ghұmys іsteuge құқyly osy elde, bіraқ kөp emes. </span></p><p><span><b>Taғy bіr artyқshylyқ</b></span><span> dep sanauғa bolady, bұl bolmaғan tүrlі bastyқtarynyң ghәne basқa da tekserushі. Kөptegen kіm ghүrgіzedі, өz biznes, tap osy problema. Bіzde broker bolyp tabylady salyқ agentі, ghәne ol avtomatty tүrde esepteydі ghәne tөleydі bіzdің barlyқ salyқtar. </span><span><b>Bіz izbavleny қarym-қatynas әr tүrlі tekserushі, nadzirayuschimi, razreshayuschimi ghәne basқa da</b></span><span> </span><span><b>organdar memleket. </b></span></p><p><span><b>Ghәne soңғy</b></span><span>, bіz aynalysamyz sүyіktі іsіmen ol arnady 20 ghyl". Treyding talap etedі үlken intellektualdyқ ghәne emocionaldyқ shyғyndar. Eshteңe salystyruғa, sen aқyl zarabatyvaeshy aқsha қashan okazyvaeshysya құқyқtaryn bolghamdar men sauda sheshіmder. Al sodan keyіn baruғa bolady k palymam ghәne teңіz ghәne azdap demaluғa ghylғy auyr eңbek kүndelіktі ghogm treyding. Bіraқ kelu үshіn osy nәtighege қaghet ұzaқ ghәne қiyn үyrenu. Dep oylamaңyz shyққannan keyіn bіrneshe beyne rolikter </span><span><b>youtube</b></span><span>, sіz bolasyz guru naryқ. </span><span><b>Kez kelgen teoriyasy talap etedі mұқiyat praktikalyқ pysyқtau</b></span><span> </span><span><b>үshіn daғdylaryn қalyptastyru</b></span><span>. Al bұl, әdette, uaқyt, ol kөptegen dayyn emes ghұmsauғa tүrlі sebeptermen: ghalқaulyқ bolmauy, uaқyt, ghұmys, olardyң aқsha ghұmsauғa oқytu. Қalay қysқartuғa bolady. Tabuғa bolady kәsіpқoylar alatyn үyretu sіzdі өzіnің sauda-sattyқ ghүyesіnde, sol arқyly kөmektesu uaқytyn қysқartu үshіn қaghet bolmaғan өnertabys menshіktі tәsіlіn sauda naryғynda.</span></p><p><span>  </span><span><i><b>Shaғyn auyryp, bіzdің ghazylushylarғa ghәne oқyrmandarғa, eger қiyn emes қoyyңyz laykter, ghasaңyz reposty men tүsіnіktemeler. Osynday erekshelіgі osy resurs. Sіzderdің kөmek ghәne nazar bіzdің eңbegі bayқausyz қalady. Sіzge kөp-kөp rahmet!</b></i></span></p><blockquote><span><i>Eger sіzge paydaly ghәne қyzyқty aқparat, onda ghazylyңyz bіzdің </i></span><span><i><b>YOUTUBE</b></i></span><span><i> ghәne </i></span><span><i><b>TELEGRAM</b></i></span><span><i> arna </i></span><span><i><b>ForeksIndeksySyrye. </b></i></span></blockquote><blockquote><span></span><a><u><i>www.youtube.com/channel/UC1N3tsoXdpGF24k7r1lKE6A/featured?disable_polymer=1</i></u></a><span></span><a><u> </u></a></blockquote><blockquote><span></span><a><u><i>https://zen.yandex.ru/profile/editor/id/5cf556fe1b104c00afef7abd</i></u></a></blockquote><blockquote><span></span><a><u> </u></a><span></span><a><u><i>t.me/ForexIndexCommodities</i></u></a><span> </span></blockquote><blockquote><span><b> Eger Sіz mүddelі oқytuda bіzdің principterge sauda bolsa, ghazyңyzdar</b></span><span> </span><span></span><a><u>stocktrader@gmail.com </u></a></blockquote><blockquote><span><i><b>Tamyz ayynda bіz қaytadan bastaymyz studentterdі oқytu. Sondyқtan ghazyңyzdar, bіz taңdaymyz, әrbіr gheke sabaқtyң ghosparyn kөmektesedі ғana emes, saқtauғa sauda depozitter, bіraқ ghәne olardy bastau tұraқty bayytu. </b></i></span></blockquote><blockquote><span><i><b>BARLYҚ SӘTTІLІK p